{"name":"Aloo Gobi","slug":"aloo-gobi","description":"Crispy vegetables sautéed in warm aromatic spices. Dinner is solved.","ingredients":[{"name":"medium russet potato","quantity":"1","additionalInstruction":null},{"name":"cauliflower florets","quantity":"4 cups","additionalInstruction":null},{"name":"lentils","quantity":"1 can (19 oz/540 ml)","additionalInstruction":null},{"name":"oil","quantity":"2 <sup>1</sup>&frasl;<sub>2</sub> tbsp","additionalInstruction":null},{"name":"Aloo Gobi Seasoning","quantity":"1 pkg","additionalInstruction":null},{"name":"water","quantity":"<sup>1</sup>&frasl;<sub>2</sub> cup","additionalInstruction":null},{"name":"tomato paste","quantity":"2 tbsp","additionalInstruction":null},{"name":"frozen peas","quantity":"<sup>1</sup>&frasl;<sub>2</sub> cup","additionalInstruction":null},{"name":"plain 2% Greek yogurt","quantity":"2 cups","additionalInstruction":null}],"totalTime":"20 min","servings":"4 servings","preparation":["Peel and dice potato into small cubes. Place in Multipurpose Steamer with cauliflower. Cover and microwave on high 5–6 min, until almost tender.","Meanwhile, drain and rinse lentils.","Heat oil in Sauté Pan over medium-high heat. Add seasoning; stir until fragrant, 45 sec. Add cooked potatoes and cauliflower; stir to coat.","Add lentils, water, and tomato paste. Reduce to simmer. Cover and cook for 8–10 min, or until potatoes are tender.","Stir in peas; cook for 1–2 min.","Divide into four bowls and top each with 1&frasl;2 cup yogurt and chopped cilantro, if desired."],"tags":[{"slug":"epic_life_lunch","name":"Lunch"},{"slug":"low_sodium","name":"Low-sodium"},{"slug":"sugar_conscious","name":"Sugar Conscious"},{"slug":"one_dish","name":"One Dish"},{"slug":"dinner","name":"Dinner"},{"slug":"lunch","name":"Lunch"},{"slug":"vegetarian","name":"Vegetarian"},{"slug":"gluten_free_e8446d0","name":"Gluten-free"},{"slug":"high_protein","name":"High Protein"},{"slug":"better_than_take_out","name":"Better Than Takeout"},{"slug":"e